{"tid":2249873,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解成日都有人幫六四解放軍洗底, 話咩北京解放軍拒絕鎮壓","createTime":"2020-10-19T15:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T06:06:08.000Z","uid":53705,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d37301991e143d5afd83ffe66e01079868f3029c","tid":2249873,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"我發覺每年都有人幫六四解放軍洗底, 話咩北京解放軍拒絕鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n事實上就係得 38軍軍長 徐勤先拒絕鎮壓<br />\n換左軍長之後, 38軍繼續鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n乜乜北京軍隊 拒絕鎮壓, 完全係都市傳說<br />\n傳傳下就當真, 但又無任何證據<br />\n我懷疑根本就係 中華膠 放出來, 用來表達 「解放軍都有好人, 唔係個個壞人」 呢D on9理論"},{"pid":"ab442c5cf436d18d66d9ecda35b61534519e0a3c","tid":2249873,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"64只係共產黨狗咬狗嘅內戰嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21b007d4f289366bdd3b040eaee52849e234101","tid":2249873,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"而家官方定論係暴動搶槍殺左軍隊，所以該殺，不是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n點都好啦，CCP就係唔會改呢種暴力鎮壓，幫刀手洗白，修改歷史真相既大方向，因為只要求穩<br />\n<br />\n洗白對呢個大方向根本無意思<br />\n<br />\n問題係方向度"},{"pid":"c03d73bc208fbfa447cb1b17a50495ba850fef7c","tid":2249873,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab442c5cf436d18d66d9ecda35b61534519e0a3c","tid":2249873,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"64只係共產黨狗咬狗嘅內戰嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"我只係唔滿意有人幫解放軍洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明解放軍 係中共政權打手, 乜乜解放軍拒絕鎮壓, 想嚇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4600fbc0eebd9d08bbdc2a5e72a1dc0a3dbdbf9","tid":2249873,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15: